  "excerpt": "Things that are urgent are rarely urgent all the time.",
  "image": "",
  "readTime": "1 min",
  "content": [
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Things that are urgent are rarely urgent all the time.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The fire alarm only goes off when there’s a fire in the oven.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "And the deadline to do your taxes only arrives once a year.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Point is, many of the things that may become urgent are often worth addressing",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "before",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "they are.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Because, of course, there’s very little upside in waiting. And there’s almost no downside in doing it",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "now",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ".",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "On the other hand, stalling until something becomes urgent carries the risk that it might not all work out.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}